{"tid":1276612,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港「沒領導」的示威令: 中共今早召開緊急會議， 討論香港局勢","createTime":"2019-07-02T03:59:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T04:26:52.000Z","uid":30561,"like":37,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a79c33b152682bd9de14281e7330a4a4bb4f86f0","tid":1276612,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T03:59:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">中國人權民運信息中心 既消息 </span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hkhkhk.com/main/messages/20432.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkhkhk.com%2Fmain%2Fmessages%2F20432.html&d=nd52c%2FRhS%2BUv0SpwCnLJ%2BtLD3cQOkzCKckuFp%2FmPVdU%3D&h=035473fb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkhkhk.com/main/messages/20432.html</a> <br />\n消息來源指，至7月2日凌晨1:30仍有中共政治局委員在值班。另外的消息來源指今天早晨政治局常委會有緊急會議討論香港局勢。 <br />\n2019年7月2日 AM 1:55 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【智慧老人】倪匡：群龍無首 大吉；BBC：沒領導的示威；北京惶恐不安</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【星 CUP 人物】倪匡： 群龍無首「大吉」</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vyY5owATwsE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DvyY5owATwsE&d=nd52c%2FRhS%2BUv0SpwCnLJ%2BtLD3cQOkzCKckuFp%2FmPVdU%3D&h=979c2120\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vyY5owATwsE</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港 「沒領導」的示威，令北京惶恐不安 </span><br />\n<br />\n冇談判代表，政府只能考慮撤回送中條例，否則示威者不會罷休。 <br />\n<br />\n無領䄂即係無得傾 <br />\n無得傾只有滿足民意 <br />\n如果唔係間唔時走晒啲人出嚟，個政府都幾頭痕 <br />\n￼<br />\n 今次令政府宣布暫緩，冇談判代表（冇戴妖，冇gphone，冇泛民，冇時代）。 <br />\n中共成日想有人帶頭招安帶頭個幾個，點知今次D維穩國安落到黎唔知招安邊個 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">BBC：一場「沒領導」的示威</span><br />\n<br />\n英國《天空新聞》（Sky News）全程直播清場過程，《英國廣播公司》（BBC）以〈香港紀念政權交接發生衝突〉（Clashes as Hong Kong marks handover anniversary）為題，由不同角度報道整日過程，包括分析利用手機程式發起一場「沒領導」的示威；《衛報》（Guardian）、《泰晤士報》（The Times）的網頁版亦在當眼地方報道事件。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">深度學習， 無領袖示威，穿洲過省。有領袖示威，寸步難行。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">同14年比較，無大台既分別<br />\n<br />\n事實又再一次證明<br />\n<br />\n無領袖示威，穿洲過省。<br />\n有領袖示威，寸步難行。</span><br />\n<br />\n計劃好，唔代表事情發展走向你所想，有時候係要改變，<br />\n所有野自發、主動，上前定後退，無人講你半句，互相合作、互相配合，無牧羊人指揮你。<br />\n<br />\n今次香港社運真係好似深度學習， 如有示威領袖，今舖可能就係冇咁既結局。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今次香港社運真係好似深度學習， 如有示威領袖，今舖可能就係冇咁既結局。 <br />\n最重要係，冇戴妖，冇gphone，冇泛民，冇時代，冇玉碎，不分化。"},{"pid":"772f51bd0db23f35743748966482dac488235c70","tid":1276612,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T03:59:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43788fc6fa8cfba5e1883b4d804569d4795eca22","tid":1276612,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T04:00:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a8f1f534098be8731bc10a5919f8cf4ab7616f7","tid":1276612,"uid":33952,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T04:00:35.000Z","msg":"陳雲琴晚講唔好被代表同談判<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e02640ac40921ffb1a5aab161b130974eb48bad","tid":1276612,"uid":30561,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"8a8f1f534098be8731bc10a5919f8cf4ab7616f7","tid":1276612,"uid":33952,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T04:00:35.000Z","msg":"陳雲琴晚講唔好被代表同談判<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T04:02:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1nf3xWY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1nf3xWY.jpg&h=5851223f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5085eefd8300db4bc02a5997dd934206d5606bac","tid":1276612,"uid":165840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T04:02:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"333d4097f7a8d314690f7ca998